  "title": "PART TIME Ladies Fashion Promoter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>JOVET by JOOP, a Singapore homegrown brand is now expanding! We are currently located at Isetan Orchard and Tangs VivoCity.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Join JOVET as a part-time Sales Promoter to assist customers at departmental stores, contributing to a positive shopping experience for our shoppers.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and assist customers to meet their fashion needs</li><li>Provide product information and recommendations to help customers make informed purchase decisions</li><li>Maintain an organized and attractive sales floor to enhance the shopping environment</li><li>Working hours 11am to 9pm</li><li>Commit to working 2 to 4 days per week as a part-time sales team member</li><li>Collaborate with team members to support store operations and customer service goals</li></ul>",
