    "description": "<p>JOVET by JOOP, a Singapore homegrown brand is now expanding! We are currently located at Isetan Orchard, Isetan Nex, Tangs VivoCity and new store opening coming up soon!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JOVET is known for smart casual styles which are stylish for work, chic for weekend, fun for travel and classy for evening occasions too!&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Join our sales team as a Retail Sales Associate, Senior Sales Associate, Outlet Supervisor and Retail Sales Manager!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>With or without experience are welcome to apply!</p>\n<p>Contact us via Whats App at 91891165 to join our team!</p>",
